Your system can be connected to any one of the following:

Hub based network: You can see everyone's traffic
Switch based network: ARP CP/ flooding

Limitation:
ARP works only in the same network, you cann't see traffic outside your network


VPN encrypt transport layer data, VPN solves the problem of hiding which two peers are communicating.

